title: Diplomat Watch Face
summary: Diplomat watch face is a mesh between technology and luxury.
description: A premium watch face designed to merge the technology of a smart watch with the look of a high end luxury timepiece. Our goal in designing this watch face was to make a watch that stuck to the original purpose of a watch. Telling time. descriptionHTML:
A premium watch face designed to merge the technology of a smart watch with the look of a high end luxury timepiece. Our goal in designing this watch face was to make a watch that stuck to the original purpose of a watch. Telling time. Although it has multiple complications, getting the information you need at a glance is very easy.

The Continuum Diplomat displays Date, Day of the Week, Month, Moon Phase and of course the time.

Works with the following Android Wear Devices

Moto 360
LG G Watch R
Sony SmartWatch 3
Samsung Gear Live

-Check out our other watch faces at Continuumwear.webflow.io for more premium faces.
